result.adr_address: 9A Hillwood Rd, Tsim Sha Tsui, Hong Kong
result.formatted_address: 9A Hillwood Rd, Tsim Sha Tsui, Hong Kong
result.name: Golden Phoenix Restaurant

reviews.text:
This is one of those restaurants that do not target tourists, but the food and ambience is excellent. There are no menus in English, and most of the staff does not speak English well, but you will enjoy the various meat dishes, which are quite big, by the way. Actually, there was one waitress who spoke decent English and she was very nice.

The place looks popular with the locals, so you may need to wait to be seated. Other than that, the service is fast.

Keep in mind that they accept only cash payments.
hum.. the steak is big , but taste is fair.
Nice childhood memory, taste like.when I was young
Taste was just okay, not bad nor good.

this restaurant is great for meat-lovers. of course, the spaghetti and soup isn't as good as pizza hut or other famous Italian restaurant but their steak is the best. you can choose how cooked the beef/pork/chicken is. the service their is ok but the toilet could be better.

result.name: 金鳳大餐廳

reviews.text: 老字號。餐湯, 牛扒具水準。餐飲冷熱同價。
無妨一去, 但不要抱太大祈望, 牛扒淡而有味(雪藏味), 黑淑汁可令你吃後喝兩公升開水, 超咸但吃不到黑椒味, 差劣
性價比高而已。。。已經足夠👏
今午去的地方是否是金鳳大餐廳的舊址，本人並不知情。現址已改為名叫~今日，是一間以自助式的素食店。
食物質素一般，服務態度不算理想。

reviews.text: 環境偏暗，經濟午餐$43.7仲要有餐包、羅宋湯、份量大👍🏻
古味港式扒房裝潢（確實雖然也可以說有些殘舊但感覺不錯），食品美味價廉，環境氣氛舒適，服務也富有人情味。尤其下午茶時間超高的性價比，人流也不多！可以安靜慢慢的享受美食！
五十幾蚊午餐，大件夾抵食，當然一分錢一分货
Extremely cheap steak of acceptable quality
第一次俾1星，按價錢 食物尚可接受。但服務連一般大排檔都不如，送錯 屈人叫錯食物。到發現餐廳自己錯 再罵人食錯。基本禮貌都唔識。垃圾！
